<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Sign Up - Event Management</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #222;
    }

    #header {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 900px;
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      white-space: normal; /* allow wrapping */
      overflow-wrap: break-word;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      user-select: none;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    #animated-text {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 700px;
      min-height: 50px; /* enough for 2 lines if needed */
      position: relative;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
      overflow: visible; /* so animation isn't clipped */
      text-align: center;
      user-select: none;
      padding: 0 1rem; /* horizontal padding */
    }

    #animated-text span {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      white-space: normal; /* allow wrapping */
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeRotate 9s linear infinite;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    #animated-text span:nth-child(1) {
      animation-delay: 0s;
    }
    #animated-text span:nth-child(2) {
      animation-delay: 3s;
    }
    #animated-text span:nth-child(3) {
      animation-delay: 6s;
    }

    @keyframes fadeRotate {
      0% {opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);}
      10% {opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);}
      30% {opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);}
      40% {opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px);}
      100% {opacity: 0;}
    }

    #why-join {
      max-width: 700px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
      user-select: none;
    }

    #auth-buttons {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 450px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .auth-btn {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 2px solid #ddd;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #222;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background-color 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .auth-btn:hover {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border-color: #aaa;
    }

    .google {
      border-color: #db4437;
      color: #db4437;
    }

    .github {
      border-color: #333;
      color: #333;
    }

    .auth-btn img {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      #header {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      #animated-text {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        min-height: 40px;
        padding: 0 0.5rem;
      }
      #why-join {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }
      .auth-btn {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section id="header">
    Become a member of Event Management today
  </section>

  <section id="animated-text">
    <span>It only takes less than a minute to create an account</span>
    <span>Join thousands managing events effortlessly</span>
    <span>Secure, fast, and easy to use</span>
  </section>

  <section id="why-join">
    <strong>Why join?</strong><br />
    Gain full access to event scheduling, real-time guest check-ins, interactive venue maps, and on-site staff coordination tools â€” all from one easy platform.
  </section>

  <section id="auth-buttons">
    <a href="/auth/google" class="auth-btn google" aria-label="Sign up with Google">
      <img src="https://www.svgrepo.com/show/355037/google.svg" alt="Google logo" />
      Sign up with Google
    </a>

    <a href="/auth/github" class="auth-btn github" aria-label="Sign up with GitHub">
      <img src="https://www.svgrepo.com/show/349375/github.svg" alt="GitHub logo" />
      Sign up with GitHub
    </a>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
